trans_title: I Am Jazz... It's My Life
introduction: Translation: I'm Jazz... It's My Life.Archie Shepp live in Paris 1983 plus Guy Le Querrec's 1967/1983 Best Puctures Book with Archie Shepp's commentaries.Bonus: Special clips at Porquerolles Jazz Festival featuring Siegfried Kessler, Diego Imbert, Michel Benita, Aldo Romano, Mino Cinelu, Stephane Guery and Serge Marsh.NTSC - All Zone.
